summary: An ordinance appropriating the sum of Three Hundred Fifty ($350.00) Dollars out of the general fund of the City of Seattle, in settlement of claim of Caroline Lundberg and C. J. Lundberg, for personal injuries received by Caroline Lundberg on the 7th day of November, 1915, while walking on the intersection of 51st Avenue South and Rainier Avenue; in said city, and authorizing the drawing of a warrant therefor.
